{"tid":769844,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"屌啊，老麥個大薯條幾時變到中薯咁","createTime":"2018-08-06T13:38:43.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-06T17:32:38.000Z","uid":26277,"like":2,"dislike":11,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"f2a902e201bade4abb23f49f1d272331a03fc11d","tid":769844,"uid":26277,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-06T13:38:43.000Z","msg":"利申好多年無加過大<br />\n<br />\n但dnlm唔好蝦我記憶力差，以前成杯加大可樂咁高<br />\n依家得一半<br />\n<br />\n啱啱想飲荔枝特飲就加咗大<br />\n跟住同佢講: 你俾撚咗個中薯我啊<br />\n<br />\n: 先生，呢個就係大薯啊<br />\n<br />\n果刻，我知道自己已經好撚老了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"425b12adabc2fec37402c055023579aec51781d0","tid":769844,"uid":15483,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-06T13:39:17.000Z","msg":"兩包細薯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e11190b675e4813c0cd73dcf9c1a44d5612bbac5","tid":769844,"uid":5793,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-06T14:09:14.000Z","msg":"啱啱出冊？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1d1d05d005c53d042a154f8dd54b30a18214c86f","tid":769844,"uid":58998,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-06T14:10:44.000Z","msg":"有成杯加大可樂咁高又誇張咗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a9bb5eb804b0ff3ff4fd1b02d64d96f7e389bddb","tid":769844,"uid":92690,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"1d1d05d005c53d042a154f8dd54b30a18214c86f","tid":769844,"uid":58998,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-06T14:10:44.000Z","msg":"有成杯加大可樂咁高又誇張咗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-06T14:16:02.000Z","msg":"我記得係成個人咁高"},{"pid":"ceaf17859e3477befe191cbf39cebfd2f5d743a3","tid":76984