e1","tid":769844,"uid":26277,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"615ddade7aba4c8943ea24d651d48dc887c6eb42","tid":769844,"uid":26277,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"d20b4e2d2d4ec81c7306f851785ef62640739c62","tid":769844,"uid":29093,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-06T14:36:09.000Z","msg":"食細薯已經夠啦  過下口癮啫"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-06T14:41:48.000Z","msg":"所以好耐無加過大同埋好多時食粟米<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-06T14:43:02.000Z","msg":"粟米我都好肯定轉咗供應商，難食勁多"},{"pid":"d2abae4a5378f89c3fdc9768b8110826636e5b62","tid":769844,"uid":57659,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-06T14:59:09.000Z","msg":"鏟薯潮文仲未出?"},{"pid":"f8667bfe1584133bc8cd51422a4ba76ff0596ee0","tid":769844,"uid":7043,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-06T15:02:24.000Z","msg":"D員工都唔知係咪有股份定點<br />\n打爆個盒有幾難<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"14dbb51a74f124d4e8e98f9d3ccadf096bb3240a","tid":769844,"uid":36157,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-06T15:58:34.000Z","msg":"舊聞變潮文？"},{"pid":"a716f40cb39ba5ce80a00dce72059a83eadff1d8","tid":769844,"uid":29929,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f8667bfe1584133bc8cd51422a4ba76ff0596ee0","tid":769844,"uid":7043,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-06T15:02:24.000Z","msg":"D員工都唔知係咪有股份定點<br />\n打爆個盒有幾難<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-06T16:07:12.000Z","msg":"純粹唔想開個包新再炒<br />\n拖得幾耐得幾耐"},{"pid":"23743ee8beb7aca74f67b3ee4f515fcff6dbe1ec","tid":769844,"uid":59832,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-06T16:18:27.000Z","msg":"我之前是在麥當勞打工的，而我產薯條的原則是：<br />\n「幹你娘塞爆」<br />\n沒錯，就是幹你娘塞爆，老子才不管甚麼公司虧損三小的，每次產的薯條就是姬芭一大包。小薯產成大薯，中薯產成巨薯。大薯買一送一，跟把整個薯條站的薯條全送給你沒兩樣。<br />\n<br />\n我還記得，我那個月上班25天，經理跑來跟我說，這個月薯條虧損二十六箱，你有頭緒嗎？<br />\n<br />\n我他媽的怎麼會知道。"},{"pid":"40bf5854993221905ccccb5347de5b158ef7a087","tid":769844,"uid":120135,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"23743ee8beb7aca74f67b3ee4f515fcff6dbe1ec","tid":769844,"uid":59832,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-06T16:18:27.000Z","msg":"我之前是在麥當勞打工的，而我產薯條的原則是：<br />\n「幹你娘塞爆」<br />\n沒錯，就是幹你娘塞爆，老子才不管甚麼公司虧損三小的，每次產的薯條就是姬芭一大包。小薯產成大薯，中薯產成巨薯。大薯買一送一，跟把整個薯條站的薯條全送給你沒兩樣。<br />\n<br />\n我還記得，我那個月上班25天，經理跑來跟我說，這個月薯條虧損二十六箱，你有頭緒嗎？<br />\n<br />\n我他媽的怎麼會知道。"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-06T16:21:33.000Z","msg":"入黎為左睇呢段文<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"82eb9b276af8663d5ca5dd5fe2f6807e747ec802","tid":769844,"uid":91813,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-06T17:32:38.000Z","msg":"以前明明係自己去個薯條櫃到任食"}]}